@WebAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5284

### 1. CREATE PERSON - RUN THIS FIRST
POST {{WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jan",
  "lastName": "Testowy",
  "email": "jan.testowy@example.com",
  "phone": "+48 123 456 789",
  "gender": 0,
  "birthDate": "1990-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "address": {
    "street": "Test Street 123",
    "city": "Warsaw",
    "postalCode": "00-001",
    "country": "Poland",
    "type": 0
  }
}

### 2. COPY THE ID FROM THE RESPONSE ABOVE
### THEN REPLACE "YOUR_PERSON_ID" BELOW WITH THAT ID

### Get person by ID
GET {{WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/contacts/persons/89885896-45f9-4a09-b94f-aee640274a7d
Accept: application/json

### Add note to person
POST {{WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/contacts/9417b665-a5d2-4490-9c02-7ad6f807e31c/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "This is my first note"
}

### Get all notes
GET {{WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/contacts/9417b665-a5d2-4490-9c02-7ad6f807e31c/notes
Accept: application/json

### Update person (PUT)
PUT {{WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/contacts/9417b665-a5d2-4490-9c02-7ad6f807e31c
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Janusz",
  "lastName": "Updated",
  "email": "janusz.updated@example.com",
  "phone": "987654321",
  "status": 0
}

### Delete note - COPY THE NOTE ID FROM GET NOTES RESPONSE
DELETE {{WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/contacts/89885896-45f9-4a09-b94f-aee640274a7d/notes/9c808150-bc71-429d-8cf2-85076e4fa03d

### Delete person
DELETE {{WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/contacts/YOUR_PERSON_ID